  <h1>Delete Your Account &amp; Data</h1>
  <p>We respect your right to have your data removed. This page explains how to permanently delete your Win The Day account and all associated data.</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Option 1 — Delete directly in the app (instant)</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <strong>Win The Day</strong> app</li>
      <li>Tap the <strong>Settings</strong> icon (top right of the Today screen)</li>
      <li>Scroll to the <strong>Account</strong> section</li>
      <li>Tap <strong>Delete Account &amp; Data</strong></li>
      <li>Confirm deletion when prompted</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Your account, habits, streaks, diary entries, and all personal data will be permanently deleted immediately.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Option 2 — Request via email</h2>
    <p>
      If you no longer have access to the app, email us at
      <a href="mailto:bellgadevelopments@gmail.com">bellgadevelopments@gmail.com</a>
      with the subject line <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong> and include the email address
      associated with your account. We will process your request within 7 days.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="note">
    Deleting your account removes all data from our servers permanently. This includes your profile,
    habit history, streaks, badges, diary entries, and any other personal information. This action
    cannot be undone. Active subscriptions must be cancelled separately through the
    App Store or Google Play.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top:40px; font-size:13px; color:#999;">
    BELL GA Developments · Perth, Western Australia ·
